      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MAGIC MIKEY (6) progressed nicely last time out to finish just half a length from the winner in second over 1611m at this track after being prominent at the bend. Well placed and there is no reason he cannot find winning ways. REGINALD (1) built on a nice third two starts back at this track with success over 1611m at this track three weeks ago, getting home by half a length. Finds a suitable race and can play a major role. GRANITE ROCK (4) is a genuine type with two minor placings from three starts this prep. Produced another good effort at his most recent run when third over 1611m at this track after he was prominent throughout. Nicely placed to take this out. MR HOLLYWOOD (7) missed the placings two runs back then didn't do any better last start when ninth over 1600m at Carnarvon. Capable of featuring prominently. CROWS (3) is not to be discounted.",
